Output ../../assets/memex_cli_entities.gif
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Framerate 15
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set FontSize 14
Set Padding 20
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "export PATH=/home/vscode/.cache/.venv/bin:$PATH"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show
Sleep 500ms

Type "memex entity list"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
Sleep 1s

Type "memex entity related Python"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
Sleep 2s
